The year 2014 was an especially notable one for the pope, and it appears this popular, charismatic leader is increasing in influence around the globe—reaching across the divide to join hands with many powerful religious and political figures in order to find common ground. What’s really going on? Pastor Doug Batchelor presses the rewind button to review the past year’s incredible developments in light of Bible prophecy and discuss what it all means for you!
